    "description": "玩家扮演奈特，一位失业、一事无成的失败者，直到有一天他发现自己有一股自身浑然不知的力量……那就是把一只脚放到另一只脚前面。<br><br>探索雾气缭绕的世界，一步一脚印地前行。《Ape Out》和《Getting Over It》团队再次发力，打造出从物理学获得灵感的原创新颖游戏玩法。一步一脚印，攀爬宁静的山脉、欣赏风景、爱上当地的动物们，并试着在虚度的生命中找寻意义。<br><br>准备好在《一步一脚印》这款真正的行走模拟器中爱上奈特。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👟 游戏内的步行体验完美符合真实物理学。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/fcf391a5930fcf1e606aa799e3d2bcee.poster.avif?t=1761065780\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/fcf391a5930fcf1e606aa799e3d2bcee.webm?t=1761065780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/fcf391a5930fcf1e606aa799e3d2bcee.mp4?t=1761065780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⛰️ 以420种节拍和基调组成的动感配乐，让游戏的世界摇曳生姿。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/83cd29be11c4a3ed5d27794771723b27.poster.avif?t=1761065780\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/83cd29be11c4a3ed5d27794771723b27.webm?t=1761065780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/83cd29be11c4a3ed5d27794771723b27.mp4?t=1761065780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >😫 在一座真实山峰大小的山上徒步前行，玩家可以按照自己的节奏探索，或更仔细地体验。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/e496f2c51bc3f543b3adea899d8d8336.poster.avif?t=1761065780\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/e496f2c51bc3f543b3adea899d8d8336.webm?t=1761065780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/e496f2c51bc3f543b3adea899d8d8336.mp4?t=1761065780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎶 全动态连身脏污系统。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/975b29f1e270b2d261c32546c7b7c59b.poster.avif?t=1761065780\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/975b29f1e270b2d261c32546c7b7c59b.webm?t=1761065780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/975b29f1e270b2d261c32546c7b7c59b.mp4?t=1761065780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤠 无法收集的帽子。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/683043bdb3c1f172c59df60b17d883cc.poster.avif?t=1761065780\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/683043bdb3c1f172c59df60b17d883cc.webm?t=1761065780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1281040/extras/683043bdb3c1f172c59df60b17d883cc.mp4?t=1761065780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
